  Roman:Sesterii:2.5:grams
  Greek:Drachma:4.3:grams
  Indian:Rupee:11.5:grams
  Hebrew:Shekel:11 grams
      But ranged from 7 to 17 grams


  1 Silver Denarius =~ 10 Grams Silver = 4 Sestertii

  so 1 Sersterii is 0.25 * 1 Silber Denarius = .25 * 10 grams

  So 1 Sestertii = 2.5 grams of silver


